@startuml seq_25_ban_mute_user
title Sequence Diagram: UC-25 Ban / Mute User

actor Moderator
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Moderation Controller" as Controller
participant "Moderation Service" as Service
participant "Restriction Repo" as Repo
participant "User Repo" as UserRepo

Moderator -> Frontend: Select Ban/Mute & Submit details
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/moderation/users/{id}/restrict {type, duration, reason}
Controller -> Service: Restrict User
Service -> UserRepo: Validate moderator permissions & target user
UserRepo --> Service: Validation passed

alt Action is Ban
    Service -> Repo: Insert Ban record
    Repo --> Service: Ban record created
else Action is Mute
    Service -> Repo: Insert Mute record
    Repo --> Service: Mute record created
end

Service --> Controller: Updated Restriction State
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Moderator: Show success & update user status UI
@enduml